  "detailed_description": "<h1>About the demo</h1><p>The demo version of Wee Tanks includes:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>30 missions from the classic campaign<br></li><li>Map editor for editing and playing maps<br></li><li>Three survival maps</li></ul><br>Not included in the demo version:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>The full classic campaign of 100 missions<br></li><li>Online Multiplayer<br></li><li>Tankey Town access<br></li><li>Workshop support</li></ul></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1797680/extras/583a9c94a95ce2dcca3053e8517aa332.poster.avif?t=1735902559\" width=600 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1797680/extras/583a9c94a95ce2dcca3053e8517aa332.webm?t=1735902559\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >TEAM UP!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight with mates. Shoot tanks with mates. Have fun with mates. Die with mates. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>Up to 16 mates.</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1797680/extras/64a2f1798b6f7a1daf9f21577ada9c18.poster.avif?t=1735902559\" width=600 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1797680/extras/64a2f1798b6f7a1daf9f21577ada9c18.webm?t=1735902559\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Enemies and bosses</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enemies... dangerous and scary. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Many variants! More than 30 I have heard.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1797680/extras/07826ee2c53502f1e40e24ad0808bfb4.poster.avif?t=1735902559\" width=600 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1797680/extras/07826ee2c53502f1e40e24ad0808bfb4.webm?t=1735902559\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Create, test and share</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create your campaign. Test it. Share it. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Steam Workshop? <strong>yes.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1797680/extras/8835be6cfb54544855b0bcf27c8f3948.poster.avif?t=1735902559\" width=600 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1797680/extras/8835be6cfb54544855b0bcf27c8f3948.webm?t=1735902559\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Tankey Town</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Earn marbles. Spend marbles. Very chill. Pimp your tank. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But breaking law is police doing pew pew.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1797680/extras/91d5dc30cbc93b549a02919fc2ef8344.poster.avif?t=1735902559\" width=600 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1797680/extras/91d5dc30cbc93b549a02919fc2ef8344.webm?t=1735902559\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Much more...</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Zombie survival mode, multiplayer Soccer or Team Deathmatch. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>There is a lot to discover. Get it now!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
